OL,3,CCouple's four year 'sewage hell' to
OL,4,Cprevent waste flooding home
OL,6,FWATCH: ITV Meridian's report by
OL,7,FCharlotte Wilkins
OL,9,FFor four years, a couple from Shoreham
OL,10,Fhave been battling Southern Water to
OL,11,Ffix a problem with a mains sewage pipe
OL,12,Fto their property.
OL,14,FIt transpired that the property,
OL,15,Fbelonging to Christine and Paul
OL,16,FJeffrey wasn't connected to the main
OL,17,Fsewer and Southern Water had been
OL,18,Fsending a tanker down to syphon away
OL,19,Fthe waste, something the couple were
OL,20,Funaware of when they bought the
OL,21,Fproperty.
