OL,3,CCouple's four year 'sewage hell' to
OL,4,Cprevent waste flooding home
OL,6,FBut during lockdown in 2020, when the
OL,7,Ftanker failed to turn up, sewage then
OL,8,Fstarted backing up in to their home.
OL,10,FSince then they say they've been
OL,11,Fconstantly given the run around by
OL,12,FSouthern Water to resolve the issue.
OL,14,FAfter countless emails, calls,
OL,15,Finvestigations carried out and the
OL,16,Fpromise of a pump to divert the waste
OL,17,Fin to a main sewer, it's still not
OL,18,Ffixed.
