OL,6,FPaul said: "They treat us so badly.
OL,7,FWe're customers but we're not
OL,8,Fimportant to them. "
OL,10,FChristine added: "This was supposed to
OL,11,Fbe our dream home. Now it's our
OL,12,Fnightmare."
OL,14,FIn a statement Southern Water said:
