OL,6,F"We're sorry Mr And Mrs Jeffrey are
OL,7,Fsuffering such inconvenience and that
OL,8,Four contractor failed to attend an
OL,9,Fappointment. All our assets in the
OL,10,Farea are working properly but we will
OL,11,Fcontinue to work with them until the
OL,12,Fissue is resolved. "
OL,14,FChristine and Paul can't let any waste
OL,15,Fwater go down their kitchen sink as it
OL,16,Fcomes back up the pipes and floods the
OL,17,Fcupboards.
